Placed on the Registry of Historic Places in
1976, the largest private estate in the history
of Beverly Hills - the Greystone Mansion
serves as a venue for city events, weddings,
films and summer day camps. The size of
the house and the grounds is sensational.
It was bought for just over millions bucks
way, way back.
The grounds & garden are exquisite &
hundreds of films have used it as backdrop.
A really exquisite history.

I'm thrilled to announce the release of my newest app, ranked #24 on the App Store charts for books (just under Jesus and the Bible 😳). This app is an augmented reality experience that complements my kids' book, "Little Bunny Dreamer." With this app, readers can enjoy Bini the Bunny and other characters coming to life within the book, playing out the story in real-time. This app is my fourth bunny-themed app available on the app stores, completing my collection. Link in bio #newapp #binithebunny #augmentedreality

The terrorists are going house to house and executing families while kidnapping others from their beds and shelters and forcefully taking them into the Gaza Strip. People can be seen begging for their lives. A baby has been found at one of the communities with parents nowhere to be found. This is the true face of the Hamas terror group, whose only goal is the cold-blooded murder of innocent men, women, and children. The world should be outraged by this war crime. Israel has every right to defend its people.
